name: Experiment Or Die #17
description: Yearlong project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of photos and personal assets. I search for interesting typography everywhere I go and can been throughout almost the entire collection so far. The DANGER photo that makes up the main part of this design was taken today at a comic shop in Louisville, KY and was an innocuous ribbon banner on top of a bookshelf. One can find the beauty in the simplest of things. IG: Nikejerk
